Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那借來的寫輪眼能抵擋這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你見識下真品與盜版的差距吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視線…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 她怎麼過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓卡卡西老師背負一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:00:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走的不是一條道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:00:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起努力過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經認為那就是自己該走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是決意踏上復仇之路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我才活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法像你和鳴人那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了佐助什麼都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…求求你 留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.14,0:01:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會想盡一切辦法幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請你和我一起留下… 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果實在不行 就帶我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然…很討人厭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我就喊人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來的真是時候啊 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你能過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之多虧你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助真的打算殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果鳴人沒有趕來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我已經被佐助親手殺死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻同是第七班的成員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說是曾經的第七班…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 小櫻 你們現在應該明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他身上浮現的是真正的殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經不是曾經的佐助了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼬的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽阿飛那傢伙說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼬的真相…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那傢伙說的是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就說過了 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既沒父母也沒兄弟的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我的理解能有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外人給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道鳴人是怎麼對你的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼流言蜚語
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都一直視你為夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便大家都準備對付佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人還是一心想著救你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼救…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對要把你…從復仇的泥濘中拯救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的復仇帷幕已經拉開了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手刃了一個鼬的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了得到那只右手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺害了多少宇智波族人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出手的是鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你逼他的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是裡四象封印術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 快遠離團藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這幹掉了木葉的高層
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫團藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助難道僅憑一人就打倒他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止 從未有過的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被玷污的宇智波得到淨化的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波從這腐朽的忍者世界超脫的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是無法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上來說 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是你們木葉長久以來的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你們所願 讓亙古以來一直被否定的宇智波
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你們的記憶中消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬斷同木葉所有的羈絆才是淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是宇智波的真正復興
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那憎恨累積而成的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造就了現在的佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助也是這個時代的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人也好 小櫻也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖不能確定 但多少也能察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都給我離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 卡卡西老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在這裡會看到不願看到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 從靜音那學來的毒苦無是殺不掉佐助的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他繼承了大蛇丸的免疫力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你已經清楚自己的心意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我已經幫你恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續戰鬥可不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動 香燐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同人質的要害一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:12:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 這是第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罷了 佐助的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂不願看到的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是殺了佐助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個快走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破綻 我可不會手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 或許…我和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該反過來才對…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷地逃啊 逃啊 苟且偷生下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後當有一天你擁有跟我相同的眼睛後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經被村民們厭惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為我體內的九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經也憎恨村裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾想過報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些塗鴉給我擦乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那小子 就是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要將這種傢伙留在村子裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代替我們想想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個混蛋 滾一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼突然來一下你要幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你好了 趕緊給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 到底為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都這樣對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連班主任也用這種眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是掃把星或黴菌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果稍有偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會像你一樣想著如此恐怖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:17:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾覺得我會一直孤單下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到同你和伊魯卡老師相遇之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高次 回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大智 吃晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不聽話呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過不准和那個孩子一起玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人…告訴你真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道十二年前封印妖狐的事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後村裡就有了條規定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是條絕對不能讓你知道的規定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只對我保密 什麼規定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能說出鳴人就是妖狐的規定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 你就是殺害了伊魯卡的雙親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅村子的九尾妖狐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所憧憬的第四代火影將九尾封印在你體內
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡所有人都瞞著你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人會認同你這樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果再可靠些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不會經歷這些痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走火入魔般的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你和伊魯卡老師 我才得救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我知道你也總是一人時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你跟我一樣我就覺得很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你都是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在回想起來 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背負著九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背負著宇智波的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.77,0:20:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們背負著相似的包袱 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是諷刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天看到你的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實想去找你聊天的 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得你應該能理解我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要問原因的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你什麼都行 讓人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我決定把你當作我的競爭對手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就成了我的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾在終結之谷說過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.63,0:22:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於一流的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的對決讓我終於有所理解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也讀懂我內心的真實想法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一流的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對我如此執著
